        {
            "id": 6007133,
            "title": "補交2024財報仍缺今年Q1財報 證交所：福懋油繼續停止買賣",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>證交所今 (4) 日表示，福懋油 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1225:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1225\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1225-TW</a>) 雖然已經補交 2024 年度財務報告，但 2025 年第 1 季財報仍未公告申報，因此，其上市股票繼續停止買賣。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6007133%2Fl%2Ffc39da76dc02fe6ac0f9530e84165647.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">補交2024財報仍缺今年Q1財報 證交所：福懋油繼續停止買賣。（鉅亨網資料照）</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>證交所說明，福懋油脂股份有限公司先前未依法令期限公告申報 2024 年度及 2025 年第 1 季財務報告，涉及證交所營業細則第 50 條第 1 項第 1 款規定情事，併案股票停止買賣。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>證交所進一步指出，該公司於今年 6 月 3 日補行公告申報去年度財報，並經會計師出具無保留意見的查核報告，但仍未公告申報今年第 1 季財報，因此對其上市有價證券繼續停止買賣。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
